# Routing Questions

11. What is routing in Flask?

Routing maps URLs to Python functions.

12. How to pass variables in a URL?
@app.route('/user/<name>')
def user(name):
    return name
13. What are route converters?

Examples:

int

float

string

path

Example:

@app.route('/post/<int:id>')
14. Difference between GET and POST?

GET → Retrieve data
POST → Send data to server

15. How to handle POST requests?
@app.route('/login', methods=['POST'])
